Description: Provides utilities to describe posterior distributions and Bayesian models. It includes point-estimates such as Maximum A Posteriori (MAP), measures of dispersion (Highest Density Interval - HDI) and indices used for null-hypothesis testing (such as ROPE percentage and pd).
